00:29:39.130 --> 00:29:41.087
So a number of you,
even if the price was just a

00:29:41.087 --> 00:29:43.627
tiny bit different might have a
preference for one rather than

00:29:43.627 --> 00:29:44.978
the other,
so without getting in trouble

00:29:44.978 --> 00:29:46.489
by putting the camera on you,
how many of you would have a

00:29:46.489 --> 00:29:48.527
preference,
if the prices were essentially

00:29:48.527 --> 00:29:51.749
the same how many of you would
have a strict preference for

00:29:51.749 --> 00:29:53.781
Pepsi?
How many would have a strict

00:29:53.781 --> 00:29:56.775
preference for Coke?
How many would have a strict

