do that.

00:38:31.389 --> 00:38:34.252
So leaving aside the specific
example of beer,

00:38:34.252 --> 00:38:38.069
you think about some product
that has some dimension on which

00:38:38.069 --> 00:38:41.130
it varies,
and we can use this model to

00:38:41.130 --> 00:38:45.239
see how competition is going to
work in that market.

00:38:45.239 --> 00:38:49.123
But now notice that this
transport cost is going to be a

00:38:49.123 --> 00:38:52.658
different interpretation.
Now, instead of being the cost

00:38:52.658 --> 00:38:55.482
of traveling that distance to go
and buy the product,

00:38:55.482 --> 00:38:58.872
what's it going to be?
It's going to be that if my

00:38:58.872 --> 00:39:02.260
preferred beer flavor is here
say, this is me,

00:39:02.260 --> 00:39:04.969
my preferred beer flavor is
here,

00:39:04.969 --> 00:39:07.698
then if I end up having to
