00:39:49.610 --> 00:39:51.923
So you're going to figure out
what happens in this story very

00:39:51.923 --> 00:39:53.349
generally, well not very
generally,

00:39:53.349 --> 00:39:55.896
but in the particular case
actually on the homework

00:39:55.896 --> 00:39:58.799
assignment, but I want you to
understand that there's this

00:39:58.799 --> 00:40:01.039
