In terms of the benefits

01:09:37.259 --> 01:09:40.718
of--the spoils of government
versus the cost of running,

01:09:40.718 --> 01:09:44.430
it's a wash for Claire Elise,
whether she enters or not.

01:09:44.430 --> 01:09:49.250
But by entering she has a half
chance of winning the election.

