it's two places away.
So in expectation it's one

01:10:04.064 --> 01:10:06.111
place away.
If she drops out,

01:10:06.111 --> 01:10:09.787
Jean wins for sure,
so the expected distance away

01:10:09.787 --> 01:10:13.539
from her of the winning
candidate is two away.

01:10:13.539 --> 01:10:15.888
Just to say it again,
so the cost and direct benefits

01:10:15.888 --> 01:10:17.470
